name: At the top
description:
Dubai. The city is also known as the 'City of Gold'. Whenever the word Dubai is mentioned, it conjures up images of luxury, modern architecture and wealth. Modern architects have been able to bring their imaginations to life thanks to it
Here is a view of the Dubai Skyline from the 145th floor of the Burj Khalifa 
Digital file : 6000 × 3703 px
